        "content": "## ðŸ”„ Automatic Reset System (Separate Workflow Branch)\n\n### Reset Schedule Options:\n- **Current:** Every 1 minute (for testing)\n- **Hourly:** Change to `0 * * * *`\n- **Daily:** Change to `0 0 * * *` (midnight)\n- **Weekly:** Change to `0 0 * * 0` (Sunday)\n- **Custom:** Any cron expression\n\n### Reset Process:\n1. **Schedule Trigger** fires at set intervals\n2. **Get all user records** from Google Sheets\n3. **Bulk reset all counters** to 0\n4. **Users can interact again** after reset\n\n### Configuration Tips:\n- **Testing:** Use minutes for quick testing\n- **Production:** Use hourly/daily for real deployment\n- **High Traffic:** Consider shorter intervals\n- **Cost Control:** Use longer intervals\n\n"
